metadata.name: WRAPPED BITCOIN
metadata.description: Wrapped in an anti-static sleeve, an OPENDIME with 1 BTC is affixed to an LED-backlit sign that says what it is: WRAPPED BITCOIN. In order to retrieve the BTC, the owner must destroy the physical artwork. The NFT, however, cannot be destroyed. The first owner of the NFT will also be the holder of the artwork. Visit my website to prove ownership and arrange delivery.
